name: Nouns showed up in a newspaper in the countryside of Brazil

metadata.name: Nouns showed up in a newspaper in the countryside of Brazil 1
metadata.description:
This NFT is a way to celebrate the 1st publication of Nouns DAO in a physical newspaper, explaining what DAO, NFTs, and cryptocurrencies are to people in the countryside of Minas Gerais, Brazil.

DISCLAIMER: 100% of sales value goes to the Nouns BR treasury.
DISCLAIMER 2: the holders of this NFT are running for a raffle of a Noun BR

You can access the newspaper in Portuguese and its English translation in our Mirror:

https://mirror.xyz/0xa42A0c4dDF7Ea5b5BE1D35A8eE7f5F037a9F9418/GnEb4aPkNtKfWylRV_rURV_KONqVUnLtHzvxm1uT0Rw
